Grimlock soars into the hole from the sky, seeing the two freaks attack
where his rocket had been, way below him. "Hmmmm, they not so bright.
Dinobots, attack" he yelled, as he cut his jets, and began to descend
towards Repugnas, transforming into his larger Tyranosaurus mode, trying
to plant both feet into Repugnas.
